metadata.name: A lady in the dark
metadata.description:
You've been walking for what feels like hours, if not days. You were exhausted from all the stepping, but your brain has been buzzing nonstop since you arrived. The next thing you know, your limbs clash, causing you to fall flat on your back. Your entire body felt numb. Perhaps it's a message that you should take a break. Your mind was racing with thoughts, but then exhaustion set in.
.
.
.
"Hello?"
